<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٦٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{دُعَاءَ الرَّسُولِ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> نِدَاءَكُمْ لَهُ بِأَنْ تَقُولُوا:</span> يَا مُحَمَّدُ! وَلَكِنْ قُولُوا: يَا رَسُولَ اللهِ!<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٦٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَتَسَلَّلُونَ مِنكُمْ}</span> ... يَخْرُجُونَ خُفْيَةً بِغَيْرِ إِذْنٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٦٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِوَاذًا}</span> ... يَسْتَتِرُ بَعْضُهُمْ بِبَعْضٍ فِي الخُرُوجِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِتْنَةٌ}</span> ... مِحْنَةٌ، وَشَرٌّ، وَعَذَابٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>